      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Conferences\" title=\"Conferences\">Conferences</a> * Computer and Games 2013</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/CG_2010\" title=\"CG 2010\">&lt; Prev</a> <a href=\"/CG_2016\" title=\"CG 2016\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg/330px-%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg/500px-%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d6/%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg/960px-%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:%E5%8D%94%E7%94%9F%E9%A4%A8.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Kyōsei-kan <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>8th International Computers and Games Conference</b>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keio_University\">Keio University</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Campus_of_Keio_University#Hiyoshi_campus\">Kyōsei-kan</a>, the Collaboration Complex <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yokohama\">Yokohama</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Japan\">Japan</a>, August 13-15, <a href=\"/Timeline#2013\" title=\"Timeline\">2013</a>. CG 2013 was held in conjunction with the <a href=\"/WCCC_2013\" title=\"WCCC 2013\">WCCC 2013</a>, <a href=\"/WCSC_2013\" title=\"WCSC 2013\">WCSC 2013</a>, and the <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Lectures\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Lectures</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Day_1.2C_August_13.2C_2013\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 1, August 13, 2013</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Day_2.2C_August_14.2C_2013\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 2, August 14, 2013</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Day_3.2C_August_15.2C_2013\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Day 3, August 15, 2013</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lectures\">Lectures</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=CG_2013&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Lectures\">edit</a><